<b>Sent:</b> Tuesday, September 2, 2025 9:21 AM<br>
<b>To:</b> Raffaella del Prete &lt;raffaellanz@icloud.com&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b> RE: REFUND Request : Contents Tower Claim: =
C90306256<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good morning, =
Raffaella.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I hope you are well =
this morning.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You will receive =
the $9,000 temporary accommodation payment in 3 to 5 working =
days.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The remaining =
amount under the temporary accommodation benefit is =
$13,820.62<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Is there a time I =
can contact you this week by phone to finalize your contents claim? the =
loss schedule provided by Asset Restore to date exceeds your sum =
insured, which means that the contents is a total
 loss as the total value of the contents damaged or destroyed is greater =
then the sum insured. I work until 1:30 so let me know when this week =
suits you.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have confirmation =
that your privacy request and the information you requested was emailed =
to you on the 25/07/25. If you can check this date and let me know if =
you have it.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding updates, =
I am more then happy to update you on the first of each month, would you =
prefer monthly contacts from me instead of =
fortnightly?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding further =
claim files, we can send you assessor reports as we receive these from =
the assessor. It would be less prudent for us to resend you the entire =
claim file each month and not efficient for us
 due to the time it takes to action these we may end up getting assessor =
reports during this process which means that report may not be added to =
that privacy request.
<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Future assessor =
reports should be the only documents we have that you are not given by =
the assessor as this would come from us.</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:=
#001272;mso-ligatures:standardcontextual">
<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:=
#001272;mso-ligatures:standardcontextual"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:=
#001272;mso-ligatures:standardcontextual">Kind =
regards,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span =
style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:=
#001272;mso-ligatures:standardcontextual"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p =
